title: Steven's Point Area Cooperative
description: The Stevens Point Area Co-op is a full-line natural foods grocery store. Shop the bulk aisle to buy just what you need, or stock your pantry with prepackaged, canned and frozen goods. You will always find fresh, local and organic produce, herbs, teas, coffees, spirits, dairy products and baked goods. Come in for the area's largest selection of vitamin, mineral and herbal supplements, as well as cruelty-free and biodegradable body care products.
